text: right St. David's Parish was created as a civil parish in Prince County, Prince Edward Island, Canada, during the 1764-1766 survey of Samuel Holland. It contains the following townships: * Lot 18 * Lot 19 * Lot 25 * Lot 26 * Lot 27 * Lot 28 It also contains Prince Royalty.
